%%{init: {'theme': 'forest'}}%%
flowchart TD
  A[Start / Boot] --> B{Have cached valid creds?}
  B -->|No| C[Call /api/bootstrap?imei=...\nheader: x-api-key]
  B -->|Yes| D[Use cached primary broker creds]

  C --> E[Read primary_broker\nusername/password/client_id\npublish_topics/subscribe_topics\nendpoints list]
  E --> F{Pick broker endpoint}
  F -->|Prefer secure| G[MQTTS HOST:8883]
  F -->|Integration only| H[MQTT HOST:1884]

  D --> F

  G --> I["MQTT CONNECT + SUBSCRIBE\nIMEI/ondemand"]
  H --> I

  I --> J["Publish telemetry\nIMEI/heartbeat (+ pump/data/daq)"]
  J --> K{MQTT disconnect / auth fail?}
  K -->|Yes| L[Backoff + re-bootstrap\nretry]
  K -->|No| M[Steady state]
  L --> C
